Muffin-Mongo
############

.. _description:

Muffin-Mongo -- MongoDB support for Muffin_ framework.

.. _badges:

.. image:: https://github.com/klen/muffin-mongo/workflows/tests/badge.svg
    :target: https://github.com/klen/muffin-mongo/actions
    :alt: Tests Status

